net.sourceforge.waters.model.base

Interface GeometryProxy

  • All Superinterfaces:
    Proxy
    All Known Subinterfaces:
    BoxGeometryProxy, ColorGeometryProxy, LabelGeometryProxy, PointGeometryProxy, SplineGeometryProxy
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    BoxGeometryElement, ColorGeometryElement, GeometryElement, LabelGeometryElement, PointGeometryElement, SplineGeometryElement

    public interface GeometryProxy
extends Proxy

    The interface base class for all objects holding rendering information.

    This is just a marker interface to be implemented by all classes that represent some kind of rendering information. These classes usually contain some geometric objects from the java.awt package.

    Author:
    Robi Malik
